metadata.name: Mushroom Land
metadata.description:
This place has changed from before.
The forest is gone and the town is now infested with mushrooms.
Big bugs crawl around day and night.
It was a long time ago that there were queens and kings.

ここは以前とは変わってしまった。
森はなくなり、今はキノコがはびこる街。
大きな蟲が昼夜なく這いずり回る。
女王様や王様が居たのはもうずっと昔の話。
